parameters: There's something written here. Let's read it.

\C[4] If someone is reading this, then I must no
longer exist in this world. The only regret I have
is not being able to deliver the flowers to you
every year without fail.

\C[4]To you who is reading this, the flower
blooming beside the altar is a precious flower
called the Sacred White Flower. If you are under
the protection of the benevolent god Baretta, I
hope you can deliver this flower to Marimari.

I wonder if this will become a farewell letter...
But I wonder what exactly happened here. There
doesn't seem to be any traces of a battle taking
place here.

For now, let's report this matter to Demetri with
the Sacred White Flower in hand.

If you have a \C[2]lock-picking tool\C[0] and a
\C[2]hairpin\C[0], you might be able to challenge
unlocking the door...

It seems like quite some time has passed, but it's
highly likely that this is the work of Rudia-san.

It looks like a room here... Could it be that
Liedis is here...? Hm?
Ah! Is that... a dead body...?!
It seems like \C[2] isn't functioning at all.

I'll just confirm the preparations. It looks like
it's going to be a tough battle.

here, right?
